Node.js Essentials - Stream copy:

- Create the files data_file.txt, new_data_file.txt in the root folder.
- Save the content "nodejs streams" to data_file.txt.
- Write a code in App.js to copy the contents of data_file.txt to new_data_file.txt.
- It is important to use streams while writing the data to the file.

--------------------------------------------------
//write your code here

const fs = require('fs');
const rs = fs.createReadStream('data_file.txt');
const ws = fs.createWriteStream('new_data_file.txt');
rs.pipe(ws);



